@NODE "Introduction" "Introduction"

Um. It's an mp3 decoder. 
It is now fast enough on an 060 to decode sounds in better than realtime,
but with some sound quality degradation.
But at present there are no audio routines for the amiga.
When AHI V3 comes along, rumour has it we will have a nice AUDIO: device,
so hang on...

This is another in a long line of Cstarware (see the faq on Darxide).

@ENDNODE


